\v 15 Wena uyazi, N\nd kosi\nd*;\x + 12.3.\x* ngikhumbula,\x + Hlu. 16.28.\x* ungihambele, ungiphindiselele kwabangizingelayo;\x + Hlu. 16.28.\x*\x + 11.20; 20.12.\x* ungangisusi ekubekezeleni kwakho; yazi ukuthi\x + 17.16.\x* ngenxa yakho ngithwele ihlazo.\x + Hlab. 69.7.\x*
\v 16 Amazwi akho atholakala njalo ngawadla;\x + Hez. 3.1,3. Isam. 10.9,10.\x* lelizwi lakho kimi laba yinjabulo njalo laba yintokozo yenhliziyo yami;\x + Hlab. 119.111,162.\x* ngoba ibizo lakho labizwa phezu kwami, wena N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu wamabandla.
\v 17 Kangihlalanga\x + Hlab. 1.1; 26.4,5.\x* emhlanganweni wabahleka usulu,\x + 6.11.\x* kumbe ngijabule; ngenxa yesandla sakho ngahlala ngedwa;\x + Lilo 3.28.\x* ngoba ungigcwalise ngentukuthelo.
\v 18 Kungani ubuhlungu bami bube khona njalonjalo, lenxeba lami lingelapheki,\x + 17.9; 30.12,15. Jobe 34.6. Isa. 17.11.\x* lisala ukuphola?\x + 14.19.\x* Isibili uzakuba njengomqambimanga\x + 1.18,19. Jobe 6.15. Isa. 58.11.\x* kimi yini, \add njeng\add*amanzi \add a\add*ngathembekanga?\x + 1.18,19. Jobe 6.15. Isa. 58.11.\x*
