\v 19 Ngakho itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Uba ubuya,\x + Zek. 3.7.\x* ngizakubuyisa, ume phambi kwami;\x + Zek. 3.7.\x*\x + 15 .1.\x* njalo uba ukhupha okuligugu kokungasizi lutho, uzakuba njengomlomo wami. Bona kababuyele kuwe, kodwa wena ungabuyeli kubo.
